Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dreams\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To now be a member, supporting the governance of the organisation that sparked those dreams, it feels surreal.\\\"\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the governance\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"those dreams\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo:PHOTOSPORT Walker said her work on the IOC Athlete's Commission was incredibly rewarding, and she was looking forward to new challenges as a member.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7810887629956972e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTOSPORT Walker\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"her work\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"new challenges\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been about giving back and being an advocate for athletes and creating change and starting new initiatives.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an advocate\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"new initiatives\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been incredible, and to have opportunity to continue to do that work in a new role is huge honour.\\\"\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opportunity\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"that work\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"a new role\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"huge honour\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walker brings expertise in technology and AI, as well as gaming and e-sports, to her new role.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999997326915848, \"rank\": 2.6701064107156e-07, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Walker\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"expertise\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"her new role\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BMX star Sarah WalkerPhoto:PHOTOSPORT NZOC President Liz Dawson said the appointment was extremely positive for both Walker and New Zealand.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999997868501623, \"rank\": 2.1167748161123265e-07, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"score\": 0.9999969696923912, \"rank\": 3.030310641723252e-06, \"text\": \"Walker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K